# Generator UI

- Workflow: dropzone → settings → generate ZIP → copy `<head>` snippet.
- Client islands only where interactivity needs it (dropzone, settings, generate, snippet).
- Validate type/size on the client; server validation remains authoritative.
- Map form fields to SPEC §3: `file`, `padding`, `background`, `presets`.
- Snippet markup must match SPEC §5.3; omit SVG `<link>` for raster sources; no manifest link.
- Generate disabled until a valid file is selected; surface API errors via `aria-live`.
